{"tid":575023,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過連續收幾十個空白SMS?","createTime":"2018-02-28T02:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T13:28:58.000Z","uid":163081,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1747794a11603eeb4773e017937fe937a67e148d","tid":575023,"uid":163081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T02:07:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我朋友（不是我）早排天未光就收到30幾個空白嘅SMS，部電話震到佢都醒埋，之後佢block左個號碼以為唔會再發生&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n點知今日又左收到另一個號碼發出嘅一堆空白SMS。<br />\n<br />\n唔知呢度有冇手足試過？係俾人狙擊騷擾定還是有其他目的呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/100655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F100655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=923592b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a1595c2de12e8077f8c8fb04429de019f700432","tid":575023,"uid":192,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T02:12:38.000Z","msg":"扑埋右"},{"pid":"953f9e78acf5a257f23d2be982d7159387373a72","tid":575023,"uid":120918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:42:38.000Z","msg":"夜晚訓教記得開燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed79ea6e99cf62fc89129a1f461dcb572d433e0","tid":575023,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:51:30.000Z","msg":"打過去"},{"pid":"03258e5faf5efade5ba9939f83e9f5d04ed45ebd","tid":575023,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:42:43.000Z","msg":"你朋友(不是你) 電話號碼係咪 50881903?"},{"pid":"c8b391e965b1d0a1bc4d5cb680ee1a4d5eda0557","tid":575023,"uid":163081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03258e5faf5efade5ba9939f83e9f5d04ed45ebd","tid":575023,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:42:43.000Z","msg":"你朋友(不是你) 電話號碼係咪 50881903?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-0